ap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-600 to-purple-600 p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-fuchsia-500/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div></div><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight\">Unique Baby Names — Rare &amp; Uncommon Names</h1><p class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Discover 15,000+ unique, rare, and uncommon baby names from around the world. Stand out with distinctive names that are memorable yet meaningful. Find the perfect uncommon name that reflects your individuality and values.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white/50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center\">Why Choose a Unique Name</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-fuchsia-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-6 h-6 text-fuchsia-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Memorable Identity</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Unique names help your child stand out and create a distinctive personal brand.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-fuchsia-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-6 h-6 text-fuchsia-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Cultural Richness</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Rare names often come from diverse cultures, broadening perspectives and celebrating heritage.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-fuchsia-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gift w-6 h-6 text-fuchsia-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M20 11v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8\"></path><path d=\"M7.5 7a1 1 0 0 1 0-5A4.8 8 0 0 1 12 7a4.8 8 0 0 1 4.5-5 1 1 0 0 1 0 5\"></path><rect x=\"3\" y=\"7\" width=\"18\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Personal Significance</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Uncommon names allow for deeper meaning and connection to specific values or stories.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-fuchsia-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-6 h-6 text-fuchsia-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Creative Expression</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Choosing unique names reflects creativity and openness to different traditions.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-50 to-purple-50/30\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center\">Unique Names by Category</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-diamond w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.7 10.3a2.41 2.41 0 0 0 0 3.41l7.59 7.59a2.41 2.41 0 0 0 3.41 0l7.59-7.59a2.41 2.41 0 0 0 0-3.41l-7.59-7.59a2.41 2.41 0 0 0-3.41 0Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-medium bg-white/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">1,200<!-- --> names</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\">Rare Gem Names</h3><p class=\"text-sm opacity-90\">Precious and semi-precious stone names that sparkle with uniqueness and elegance.</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl\"><p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900\">Jade</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Precious green stone</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Spanish</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl\"><p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900\">Onyx</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Black gemstone</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Greek</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl\"><p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900\">Opal</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Precious stone</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Sanskrit</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl\"><p class=\"font-bold text-gray-900\">Topaz</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Golden gem</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Greek</p></div></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700\" href=\"/names/religion/islamic/1\">Explore more <!-- -->rare gem names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=