sider Cultural Sensitivity\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"When choosing names from other cultures, research their meaning and significance to ensure respectful usage. Some names have religious or ceremonial importance that should be honored appropriately.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Quick Guidelines:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-fuchsia-600 font-bold\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],\"Test the name with your surname for flow and rhythm\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-fuchsia-600 font-bold\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],\"Consider potential nicknames and abbreviations\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-fuchsia-600 font-bold\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],\"Check for unintended meanings in other languages\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-fuchsia-600 font-bold\",\"children\":\"✓\"}],\"Ensure it won't cause constant misspellings or corrections\"]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center\",\"children\":\"Unique Names FAQ\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\",\"children\":\"How unique is too unique for a baby name?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"A name becomes 'too unique' when it's difficult to pronounce, spell, or might cause embarrassment. Aim for distinctive but accessible—names that are unusual yet still functional in daily life. The sweet spot is memorable without being confusing.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\",\"children\":\"Should I worry about my child being the only one with their name?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Some children enjoy having a unique name and the individuality it brings. Others might prefer something more common. Consider your child's potential personality and how the name will be received in school and professional settings.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\",\"children\":\"How can I test if a unique name works?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Say it aloud with your surname, imagine it on a resume or business card, and test it with friends and family. A good unique name should feel natural when spoken and written in all contexts.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\",\"children\":\"What about unique spellings of common names?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Creative spellings can backfire—your child may spend a lifetime correcting people. It's often better to choose a genuinely unique name than to alter a common one. Unique takes the heat off the spelling issue entirely.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"FAQPage\\\",\\\"mainEntity\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"How unique is too unique for a baby name?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"A name becomes 'too unique' when it's difficult to pronounce, spell, or might cause embarrassment. Aim for distinctive but accessible—names that are unusual yet still functional in daily life.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"How can I test if a unique name works?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Say it aloud with your surname, imagine it on a resume or business card, and test it with friends and family. A good unique name should feel natural when spoken and written in all contexts.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"What about unique spellings of common names?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Creative spellings can backfire—your child may spend a lifetime correcting people. It's often better to choose a genuinely unique name than to alter a common one.\\\"}}]}\"}}]]}]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"py-12 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-600 to-purple-600\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6\",\"children\":\"Discover Your Perfect Unique Name\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg text-fuchsia-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\",\"children\":\"Explore our curated collection of 15